title: Ubuntu 10.04 Lucid Lynx - Netbook - "Slim" remix
description:
Ubuntu Netbook slim is a original distribution Ubuntu, with Netbook Gnome environnement, but, slim designed a slim environnement, without preinstalled software (no software and services installed after install, you can choose all the  softwares).
This release we can installed in all languages. ;)

Website project Slim-like&EasyNux : http://steelix.org
